title: Was a Baby Born Alive at 23 Weeks ‘Thrown in the Trash’?
subtitle: Pro-life commentators highlighted the 2006 Florida case of Sycloria Williams in September 2019.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In 2006, an abortion-clinic owner cut the umbilical cord of a baby born alive before "throwing" her in a biohazard bag and putting her remains in "the trash."
